    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const jobData = $(\"Get Job Info\").item.json.data[0];\nconst candData = $(\"Get Candidate Info\").item.json.data[0];\nconst resumeText = $json.text;\n\nconst prompt = `You are a technical recruiter evaluating candidate fits.\n\nJob: ${jobData.Job_Opening_Name}\nJD: ${jobData.Job_Description}\n\nCandidate: ${candData.Full_Name}\nResume Text:\n${resumeText}\n\nEvaluate and return ONLY a valid JSON object matching this structure:\n{\n  \"rating\": \"Green\" | \"Yellow\" | \"Red\",\n  \"score\": 0-100,\n  \"summary\": \"short summary\",\n  \"gaps\": [\"gap 1\"],\n  \"questions\": [\"question 1\"]\n}`;\n\nreturn {\n  json: {\n    model: \"qwen2.5:7b\",\n    prompt: prompt,\n    stream: false,\n    format: \"json\"\n  }\n};"
      },
      "id": "18",
      "name": "Build Ollama Payload",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
